1 Week Ago





Different sources told SaharaReporters that intensive lobby has been the order of the day among top politicians in the state, especially those from Gusau’s senatorial district. The source added that most of the politicians are lobbying Governor Matawalle through the “kingmaker of the state”, Senator Yerima Sani. “There are five people involved who are currently vying for the seat. As the kingmaker of the state, Senator Yerima Sani, three of the candidates have since approached him to lobby for the potentially vacant seat,” one of the sources told SaharaReporters. 



